{"tid":1831033,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"昂山素姬緬語聲明 fb自動繙譯擺烏龍  習近平變Mr.Shithole","createTime":"2020-01-20T05:52:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T06:59:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c566b82ee2f8d668180e913cd7e58e316869b118","tid":1831033,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T05:52:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200120/R67P5CACOSNMLJIZD2BKCSKZDM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200120%2FR67P5CACOSNMLJIZD2BKCSKZDM%2F&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV96GvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=e2fc22d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200120%2FR67P5CACOSNMLJIZD2BKCSKZDM%2F&h=ee61e2b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200120/R67P5CACOSNMLJIZD2BKCSKZDM/</a><br />\n<br />\n昂山素姬緬語聲明 fb自動繙譯擺烏龍 <br />\n習近平變Mr.Shithole<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n習近平上周末到緬甸進行國是訪問，向緬豪擲數十億美元換得緬方隆重相迎，豈料最後卻被社交平台facebook玩殘。緬甸官方及領導人昂山素姬用緬文在fb發表習到訪的消息及聲明，但fb自動譯成英文時，習近平竟變成「糞坑先生」（Mr. Shithole）；連緬國新聞網站也跟着譯為「招待糞坑主席的晚宴（Dinner honors president Shithole）」。輿論譁然，fb急發聲明道歉，稱「技術原因」出錯並已解決。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：「早安」譯「宰了他們」 中東人被當恐怖分子<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200120/large/1579449209_2c75.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200120%2Flarge%2F1579449209_2c75.gif&h=2368e8d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n習近平訪緬期間與緬方會談。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n習近平這次出訪緬甸，是中國最高領導人近20年來首次到訪，因緬方極度期盼中國投資，當局對習到訪相當重視；緬國總統溫敏（Win Myint）及國務資政昂山素姬分別與習會晤。習乘坐的專機進入緬甸領空、結束訪問回國時，緬方派多架戰機升空護航。習訪緬兩天，在緬出席12場活動，見證兩國簽署29項各領域合作文件；大部份涉中方投資緬甸。<br />\n<br />\nfb急致歉修正錯誤<br />\n<br />\n習近平訪緬期間，緬國官方及昂山素姫本人，分別用緬語在fb發表有關消息，但fb將這些緬文繙譯成英文時，「習近平」被譯成「糞坑」（Shithole），昂山素姬的臉書帖文出現「Mr.Shithole, President of China arrives at 4 PM」（中國國家主席糞坑先生於下午4時抵達）、「President of China, Mr. Shithole, signed a guest record of the house of representatives」（中國主席糞坑先生在下院人民院貴賓簿上簽名）等句子，讀者見之無不愕然。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200120/large/1579449207_1a0b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200120%2Flarge%2F1579449207_1a0b.gif&h=7f1bc54a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n緬甸官方fb貼文誤把習近平譯成Mr.Shithole。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200120/large/1579449208_7a0a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200120%2Flarge%2F1579449208_7a0a.gif&h=3e51dddf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n習近平、緬甸總統溫敏（左二）、國務資政昂山素姬（右二）出席中緬建交70周年紀念活動。路透社<br />\n系統自行猜測近音詞<br />\n<br />\n更有甚者，緬甸當地新聞網站《伊洛瓦底》（Irrawaddy）頭條也出現「招待糞坑主席的晚宴」（Dinner honors president shithole）譯文。未知fb的錯誤持續了多久，本報記者昨嘗試查找fb誤譯但不果。事件被路透社等截屏報道，轟動一時。18日下午，fb就此事發聲明稱，事件為技術原因，已獲解決，「正努力確定事故原因，以確保問題不再發生」，又稱事件「不代表我們產品該運作的方式，我們對為此造成的冒犯真誠道歉」。中國官方對事件無回應。<br />\n<br />\nfb還解釋，在緬甸文繙譯資料庫中沒習近平的姓名，這種情況下系統會猜測字詞，並用相似音節的字詞替換。緬甸文中以xi和shi音節開頭的字詞，同樣會被繙譯成「shithole」。有電腦專家表示，不少著名的社交網站都附有自動繙譯功能，但主要提供中、英、法、德、意、日、俄等大語種互譯，繙譯小語種或未必如意。緬甸語屬漢藏語系藏緬語族，在緬國有約3,200萬人使用，但國際社會上則鮮有使用。<br />\n<br />\n由朱克伯格創辦的fb是美國最流行的社交網站之一，據稱全球用戶逾10億。與其他外國熱門社交網一樣，fb在中國被列入封殺名單，網民要翻牆才能使用。朱克伯格的妻子是中國人，他一直想進軍中國巨大的網絡市場，為此曾百般努力，但面對中共嚴厲的意識形態控制，始終未能如願。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/facebook<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200120/large/1579449208_0984.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200120%2Flarge%2F1579449208_0984.gif&h=1bb7515a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c98b979cb720df1f13ff024a8ab5a87693e57aed","tid":1831033,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T05:54:32.000Z","msg":"條臭西都有今日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25d4dae6c32b28db8b4123aa7789a191ef111344","tid":1831033,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T05:56:48.000Z","msg":"fb又入唔到蛆蝈了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05c68de610629452c7f048519d7df42af85058cb","tid":1831033,"uid":2267,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T05:57:43.000Z","msg":"Mr. Shithole<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17e0d24b0940f35e2f13acd3b7959d1f2bd4876d","tid":1831033,"uid":46500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T05:58:48.000Z","msg":"應景呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e5560ab4277f0ec6abd2b624afa63ef3833102e","tid":1831033,"uid":34517,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T05:59:44.000Z","msg":"相關新聞：「早安」譯「宰了他們」 中東人被當恐怖分子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9a4cd10ae2c87c5f0ec104a50cd1a0d1fa1369e","tid":1831033,"uid":105518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T05:59:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8cfe370d93a8b584433ab452db309760dce23e8","tid":1831033,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b9a4cd10ae2c87c5f0ec104a50cd1a0d1fa1369e","tid":1831033,"uid":105518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T05:59:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T06:01:34.000Z","msg":"改名改得咁快<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"118fcf74347ecb1b059af9d49495cc397ede034e","tid":18310